            <h2>What is a CTF?</h2>
            <p>Capture The Flag (CTF) is a type of computer security competition where participants solve cybersecurity challenges to find hidden "flags" - typically strings of text that serve as proof of completing a challenge.</p>
            <p>CTF challenges cover a wide range of categories including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Web Security</li>
                <li>Cryptography</li>
                <li>Reverse Engineering</li>
                <li>Binary Exploitation</li>
                <li>Forensics</li>
                <li>OSINT (Open Source Intelligence)</li>
            </ul>
